ssh on Mac/Linux    
ssh is one of the most important function. It allows you to control a remote machine, all using a command 
line.

ssh using windows:
Putty does not accept hte pem file format so we need to convert it using puttygen.exe software so putty can accept it.

So to connect to putty everytime you log out of the AWS instance follow the below steps:
1. Start the ec2 instance.
2. Open putty and re-enter the IPv4 Public IP key and configure the putty by entering the converted pem key.

 